Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.97,1:50:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the divinity of all that exists radiates forth.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.23,1:50:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's effulgent.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:18.71,1:50:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens is you let go of the ego progressively.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:22.77,1:50:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly there's a collapse.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.53,1:50:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a feeling as though you're dying.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.02,1:50:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The feeling of the dying is merely the illusion of the personal self.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:33.18,1:50:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The real you is not dying.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:35.69,1:50:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, the real you is not even capable of dying.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.85,1:50:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So any time you think you're dying, you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.14,1:50:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The real you can't die.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.98,1:50:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So feeling that one is dying is the dissolution of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:55.18,1:50:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And it can be quite terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.86,1:51:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, having let go of everything, the only thing left is the sense of self.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.67,1:51:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The sense of self, all that was left of that as the source of life,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.81,1:51:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that within me is the source of life itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.68,1:51:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I turn over life to God, I will surely die.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:19.09,1:51:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And then came the knowingness from some lifetime, the aura of the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.09,1:51:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So the value of the aura of the teacher is
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.85,1:51:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the knowingness transcends all eons of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:28.85,1:51:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The knowingness exists as a vibration and a frequency.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.68,1:51:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And then when it's needed, it shines forth.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.81,1:51:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So in that state, I thought I have turned
Dialogue: 0,1:51:39.38,1:51:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,everything over to divinity, there's nothing left except
Dialogue: 0,1:51:43.73,1:51:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,life itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:46.09,1:51:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This, too, I must surrender to thee, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.77,1:51:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This, too, my life, I must surrender to thee.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.67,1:51:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I surrendered the core of the ego,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:56.35,1:52:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,which is convinced that it is the source of your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:01.18,1:52:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And a terrible state of terror befell me as I felt myself dying.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:07.38,1:52:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And then on the other side, suddenly the door of splendor,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:11.60,1:52:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,opened up and all of existence shone forth as the revelation of the presence of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:19.85,1:52:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All that is, is a reflection of the radiance of divinity in its infinite beauty and perfection.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.13,1:52:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:29.47,1:52:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is then the completion of the road of the mystic.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.67,1:52:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Illuminated state.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:37.18,1:52:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The emergence into a oneness.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.75,1:52:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is a radiance and a shining
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.22,1:52:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,forth. There is a radiance and a shining forth.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:46.06,1:52:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,People say, how do I know when I've reached it?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.10,1:52:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's self-revealing.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.34,1:52:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The divinity of all that exists shines forth.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:56.17,1:52:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The divinity of this room, of the people here.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.02,1:53:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The divinity of this person here, the divinity of all of you out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:04.82,1:53:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The divinity of the essence of this meeting and our reason for being here.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:12.21,1:53:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We are each other's blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.17,1:53:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we all represent consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.32,1:53:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Divinity expressing itself through the human domain is that which we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:24.22,1:53:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,To merely be here, we are serving God and serving each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:28.57,1:53:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We are serving divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.89,1:53:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So we acknowledge the divinity of thy presence, O Lord, and give thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:37.14,1:53:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:41.23,1:53:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:45.06,1:53:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's next?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:46.10,1:53:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to take a quick break.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.26,1:53:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to take a quick break right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:51.06,1:53:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to start lighting up, you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:52.93,1:53:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll take it'll be about 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:56.06,1:53:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to take a quick break, then we're going to do questions and answers.
